info.description:
# Modulo de Log para Splunk da Loja Integrada

## No __init__.py de sua app configure o Logger:

from logger import splunk

splunk.configure_logger(splunk_indice_name, app_version)


# Uso:

## Exemplos de chamadas para logar:

 splunk.loginfo('account', 'workflowtype', 'workflowinstance', msg, {"customField1": 3})
 splunk.logdebug('account', 'workflowtype', 'workflowinstance', msg, {"customField1": 3})
 splunk.logwarn('account', 'workflowtype', 'workflowinstance', msg, {"customField1": 1, "customField2": "2"})
 splunk.logerror('account', 'workflowtype', 'workflowinstance', msg, {"customField1": 1}, ex)
